name: Ampersand Limited Edition Print
description:
Limited Edition of 25. 
Archival digital print on Hahnemühle 305 gsm heavy weight matt paper. 
Signed and numbered on front by Louis Savage 
Image size 31 cm x 24.5cm 
Paper size: 41.5cm x 29.7cm

Comes with signed and dated Certificate of Authenticity.

International Shipping.

Custom framing and mounting available, please contact for more information.

Ordering/Delivery 
All orders are processed securely through Paypal. We aim to dispatch orders within 2 business days, however on rare occasions this may extend up to 7 business days. Delayed orders will be notified by email directly.

Artwork must be returned in its original condition and packaging. 
Return shipping will be at the customers expense and it is recommended to use a trackable shipping method as undelivered returns will not be accepted for refund.

On receipt of the Artwork your return will be processed and the amount owed will be refunded to your original source of payment (less shipping costs) within 7 business days of your merchandise return.
